line":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[284,12009,25179,157368],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"唐朝还是西都长安，东都洛阳。洛阳从“东都”变成“西京”肇始于五代，此时开封成为“东京”，宋代开始定型。 偏偏唐朝之前定都于洛阳的莫名其妙是“西晋”？于前于后都莫名其妙，汉唐都曰长安为西，洛阳为东，为啥搁晋朝这，洛阳就成西了？ 较之于后，拓跋氏定都于洛阳称之曰“北魏”，宋齐梁陈四朝皆定都于建康曰之“南朝”。北宋建都开封曰之为“北”，南宋行在临安曰之“南”。比较前后从来没有洛阳相对于南京曰“西东”，只有晋朝孤例，这是为何？实在不伦不类。 晋于汉唐之间，洛阳依前依后都应是“东都”，何以冠之西晋？衣冠南渡之后应以之后南朝为例，循之以南，何谓之“东”？遑论后世南唐南宋南明？何以晋曰“东晋”？ 三国·吴可相对于成都曰“东”，然晋循吴例？"},"attached_info":"Cj4InI2S3O3S6d4XEAMaCDk4NzIzMjIxIPumgKYGMAA4fkAccgk2MTM5OTMzNTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-fd9c7646219fe0d7a4d0f4fa7a352021_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1742048315.758669","card_id":"Q_8857917219","target":{"id":8857917219,"title":"古代政权是怎么解决缺少战马的问题的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/8857917219","type":"question","created":1736140000,"answer_count":16,"follower_count":72,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAInI2S3O3S6d4XEAMaCTExMjc0ODA0MiDgye27BjAAOEhAHXIKODg1NzkxNzIxOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]}],"description":{"time":"2025-03-15 22:18:36"}}